  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan <br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Kōsoku Clan, Level 4+ <br />You fight for others, putting your speed to the test to protect them. You gain the following benefits;</p><ul><li>Increase your Will of Fire maximum to 5.</li><li><p>When an ally within 30 feet of you would be the target of an attack, as a reaction you may impose the attack as if you were the target and attempt to clash it, regardless if the jutsu has the clash keyword or not. On a success the attack is completely negated and the target gains the concussed condition. You are considered to cast a taijutsu of a rank determined by your movement speed.</p><ul><li>D-Rank:0-60 feet</li><li>C-Rank:65-95 feet</li><li>B-Rank:100-195 feet</li><li>A-Rank:200-295 feet</li><li>S-Rank:300+ feet</li></ul></li></ul>",
